---
title: Corn Chip-Crusted Chicken Burger with Spiced Fries & BBQ Mayo
description: Add some fun to your chicken burger by crusting it in corn chips and frying it up into a mouth watering sensation. To give it a little kick
we’ve included our barbecue spice blend to the mix. Put it on a bun and serve with spiced fries and creamy slaw. It’s a meal that’s a
delight to make and eat!

